==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Mythologize
<hw>My*thol"o*gize</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>mythologiser</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>To relate, classify,
and explain, or attempt to explain, myths; to write upon
myths.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>To construct and propagate myths.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Mythologizer</ent>⟦br⟧
